<br>
And so it makes more sense to you that Warriors should always be the second (or third) choice as a tank instead?  Okay, I want better solo ability and some spells to compensate.  Or better yet, FD.<br>
<br>
Do you know why Paladins will have any more attraction over a Warrior as a tank?  Three primary reasons.  They can stun to generate agro, they can heal, and they can root park.  With high end gear their AC is effectively the same as a Warrior's and for experience groups the difference in HP is not a major factor.  And with high end 2handers the DPS difference is minor.<br>
<br>
Your spells are your attraction more than anything else.  Take away a Paladin's spells and the Warrior would clearly be the better choice.  But that isn't going to happen.<br>
<br>
If a Warrior can't noticeably take damage better than a Paladin, there is no reason to have the Warrior.  Thanks for wanting to condemn us to exactly the position you were in for Kunark.  No thanks, we pass.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uaragirlancot.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aragir Lancot</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 30<br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/9/02 11:44:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1056.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Warrior issues</span><hr size=1> Glatius,<br>
My apologies, I tried to make it clear that I don't want paladins to relegate warriors to the ash-heap.  I favor class balance, where a group that has a slot open and has a Warrior, a Paladin, and a Shadowknight campaigning for the position will have a hard choice on their hands.<br>
<br>
I don't, however, feel that the way to reach that balance is by making the warrior head and shoulders above the other two classes.  I geniuinely think that the changes I mentioned in my previous post would help reach this balance, and if you think that the ONLY way for this balance to be reached is for warriors to be the ultimate tank, then I'm afraid we will just have to agree to disagree.<br>
